### Typische Fehler / Common Errors

| Fehler / Error | Lösung / Solution |
|----------------|------------------|
| `rg: command not found` | `sudo apt install ripgrep` |
| `bash: bad version` | `brew install bash` (macOS) |
| `Permission denied` | `chown -R $USER .` |
| `git: command not found` | `sudo apt install git` |

